<plot>Staring down the barrel of his own revolver, divorce attorney Tom Chaney prepares to die and prove once-and-for-all there is NO God. When a determined door-to-door evangelist refuses to leave the gunman in his misery, Tom takes the young preacher hostage and a deadly debate over seeing and believing begins. But the surprises are many and by the time each player reveals their true hand, the lines between heaven and hell, good and evil, reality and fiction collide. And when the last shot is fired, the only question left is, "Will God be there?"</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?187915</url></doc>
